        "Name": "Ascension Tips: Economy and Operations",
        "Ver": "3.7",
        "Tuts": [
            {
                "Image": "TutorialPage_10006401.png",
                "Desc": "The total amount of Gold Coins acquired in a match will greatly influence the match's outcome.<br>Remember to keep 50 Gold Coins to accumulate interest, which grants 5 Gold Coins in interest per Node. Every little bit adds up!"
            },
            {
                "Image": "TutorialPage_10000801.png",
                "Desc": "Reasonable allocation of Gold Coins:<br>1. Moderate Store refreshing in the early game. Prioritize saving interest and increasing your level to find higher-cost characters in the late game.<br>2. Non-core characters in the lineup do not need to aim for 3 stars, as 2 stars are sufficient, which saves a certain amount of Gold Coins."
            }
        ],
        "Type": 5,
        "Order": 654
