        "Name": "Ascension Tips: Equipment Advancement",
        "Ver": "3.7",
        "Tuts": [
            {
                "Image": "TutorialPage_10006501.png",
                "Desc": "There are 8 types of basic equipment, and each type corresponds to an attribute. For example:<br>• The Folding Knife can increase On-Field Strength, suitable for on-field damage dealers.<br>• The Peace Pistol can increase Off-Field Strength, suitable for off-field damage dealers.<br>• Roller Skates can increase SPD Amplification, suitable for speed-type characters."
            },
            {
                "Image": "TutorialPage_10000902.png",
                "Desc": "The effect of Advanced Equipment is usually related to the effect of the Basic Equipment in its synthesis formula. For example:<br>Folding Knife (On-Field) + Lucky Star (Lucky Strike Rate) = High-frequency Chainsaw (Significantly increases the Lucky Strike Rate of on-field characters)<br>Flower of Life (HP) + Batch Produced Armor (Armor) = Analgesia Chip (When healing a target, reduces the DMG they take)"
            }
        ],
